Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------text-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的名字是古屋萤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天开始上高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我有个以引为豪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一个作为班委团结着班级的很厉害的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,虽然因为太过认真找不到女朋友很可怜就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:25.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,古屋君 又在同一个班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:28.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川同学 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:29.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:31.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我哥哥承蒙你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么客气 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 只是客套话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:45.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥 这人谁 只是同学么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,关系好么 还有其他女性朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:49.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 萤 很没礼貌诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢你哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:53.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈? 你在说啥? 这很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:55.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 这家伙是兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是挺好的吗 挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以你是我哥的什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:02.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:08.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,莫非难道说 你们两个在交往中?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 我们只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我早就觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:14.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,暂时哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前我表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是没有得到回应 所以说是暂时啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:26.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这家伙在耍你玩 怎么回应早就想好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 快点拒绝她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,让她怀有希望很可怜的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤… 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是吖古屋君 要拒绝的话就快点吖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:46.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 我 并 并不是对皆川同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拒绝她 拒绝她 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也 也不是不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我在担心你啊为什么就不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你在被玩弄 就算交往也只会受伤而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:05.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤 并不是说要交往哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我这是被拒绝了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,女朋友什么的不需要吧 因为有我就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 皆川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我没法轻松说出交往吧这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为交往之后那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,结婚什么的 没有经济能力的话孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我们的事情你已经考虑到这种地步了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,并不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,当然不是这样的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是因为我哥人比较认真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是啊 真的很认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:33.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以才喜欢吖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我再试着等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小萤 能先帮我看着么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可以 我不会把哥哥让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没关系的哟 我会一起疼爱你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是讨厌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我没什么特别喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能热衷的兴趣和爱好也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我自己都觉得自己是无聊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是大家真的有那么多喜欢的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:11.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看起来喜欢星星呢 要不要加天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 并没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 嘛 只是聊聊天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,决定了要加什么社团了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:23.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那要不要来看看星之管弦乐呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊嘞 玩笑过头啦!? 啊嘞嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看星星很开心么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那是当然啊 这么好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是只是看的话不会厌倦么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,会厌倦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有别的特点什么的了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有! 简单地说就是天文部很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,现在脱单率高达100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么样 是不是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前辈你并不是那么喜欢星星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那为什么要在天文部?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:02.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 你看 我喜欢天文部的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶 还有些什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,难道说没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜托了! 反正你没有其他其他想加的社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我说一个让你对星星感兴趣的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:18.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那块区域有一个叫做角宿一的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看起来是一个非常大的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:29.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但其实是两颗相互环绕吸引的星星哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,两颗星星共同努力的话就可以发出如此耀眼的光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是不是有点哲学味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:35.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有兴趣了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn方正喵鸣\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明完全抄的学长的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有其他的了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn方正喵鸣\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明感觉受教了很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看火星时吃的章鱼烧 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:55.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已经毕业了的前辈说什么火星人应该就像章鱼一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以就一边看火星一边烤章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:02.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn方正喵鸣\bord1.2\c&H00050606}然后一边看火星一边烤章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是前辈一直在看火星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我一个人大口大口地吃完了
Comment: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是前辈一直在看火星 所以我一个人大口大口地吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}然后前辈就超级生气 本来他平时脸就好可怕了啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}其他的比如还有秋天赏月呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,对这个人而言 天文部是真的非常喜欢的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:15.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏天一边热火超天地讲着外星人的恐怖故事一遍吃棒冰什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已经跟星星没有关系了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也能像这样热衷于什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:23.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加贺也来嘛 肯定很会有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我没有什么特别喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一边觉得这样的自己很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一边寻找着自己喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这就是我在寻找的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:44.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,总而言之我 想要多看看这份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:49.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,邻座的上根同学 总是回避着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:09.82,title - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord3.5\3c&H00474849\fs70\b0\fad(0,1000)\pos(1000,595.619)\b1}隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根还不回家么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,马 马上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不愿和我对上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我做了什么不好的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,还是赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚 刚田君!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:24.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,现在 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的隐形眼镜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:29.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我出去的时候会注意不踩到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:32.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想要你陪我一起找啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明白了 一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实我没被讨厌么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你经常掉隐形眼镜么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:42.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如想要擦擦汗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这汗确实不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实你有话想对我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我已经做好准备 尽全力回应上根的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想说什么就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,既然你都说道这种份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,应该已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,现在暂时 还没什么头绪就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前上课的时候呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我因为眼睛不好正在苦恼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你把笔记借给我过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那件事怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为 好温柔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是多管闲事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有注意到真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才没有! 不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找隐形眼镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,至少请让我帮你找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 找到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:51.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答复?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 也没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的感情 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也只是想传达给你而已… 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你这意思是 想看到我的诚意么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是 想知道刚田的想法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:07.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果这样能得到你的原谅的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:19.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我其实 一直都理解不了女生的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 没那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果再接近你的话 肯定会给你添更多麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么没用的我 以后还是承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哼～ 隐形眼镜找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:41.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎么哭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚才你是 能和我交往的意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交往?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顾的话 肯定是要交往的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,谢谢——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没事吧 上根??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我说的话很奇怪么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 我这边才是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我还没 好好的告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7}注释：告白在日语本意是说出实话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:12.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 有什么话想说就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,未报的雨 落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 没带伞么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,同班的菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,几乎没和他说过什么话
Comment: 0,0:01:04.04,0:10:37.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H007D7D7D\bord5\blur3\fs90\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b0\fad(500,0)\pos(989.943,489.886)}雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:38.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,借给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 跑回去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:42.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为感觉很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,中途还是一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 和女生一起回家的话会很难堪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也没有 和高野一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:02.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 和我这种人传不出什么绯闻的意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:03.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,肩膀淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:08.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那再靠近点?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 再近点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 不会不好意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和男生 这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 也没人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 要是被喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:27.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到了之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 我也没这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎么笑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,恋爱这种事情我不是太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你要是被表白了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这种人不存在的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是假设啦 假设你被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概会拒绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为 为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:53.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为 对我这种人表白 他肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我又不可爱 又阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才没有这种事!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野你帮别人做卫生什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,每天照顾班里的青鳉鱼之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我 对高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我要在这里坐公交了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚才 你对我说了什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样 那拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:28.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,恋爱么… 对我来说太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君这么温柔 肯定很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:33.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,阿勒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚才 要对你说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然还是决定要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 我对高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你是在 鼓励我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:58.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:03.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我在这里下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:10.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶? 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君这人 真是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,作为借伞的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,给他做点曲奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.08,title - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord3.5\3c&H00474849\fs60\b0\fad(500,0)\pos(641.334,456.952)}至近距离恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 至近距离恋爱
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也会觉得很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}此时此刻也在想念着你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}喜欢与讨厌相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的概率的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}还是跨不出这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}我们的关系可以说是暧昧模糊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}虽然无聊但还是希望能感受到属于我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}要珍视这份感情
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.94,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.11,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:40.61,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.45,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.91,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:52.29,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:57.71,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:04.26,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:09.43,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明日も目が覚めたとき
